bio: Crypto Enthusiast  with experience in Crypto Space Enthusiast | 2017 - Present
impactDescription: As an Optimism ecosystem user, I go beyond personal benefits. I promote growth by onboarding users, giving feedback, and creating awareness. This strengthens the network effect and attracts developers. I also educate and advocate for Layer 2 solutions, making them accessible. Using these solutions, like DeFi and NFTs, supports the ecosystem's economic health.
